    <section id="approach" class="section container">
      <div class="kicker">How we work</div>
      <h2>From intent to signed, shipped, and settled</h2>
      <div class="grid col-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>1) Brief & Feasibility</h3>
          <p class="muted">Define the need (product, volume, target markets), verify compliance rules, and confirm financing instruments.</p>
          <h3>2) Sourcing & Structuring</h3>
          <p class="muted">Source qualified suppliers/buyers, align specs and incoterms, shape a de‑risked commercial structure.</p>
          <h3>3) Approvals & Logistics</h3>
          <p class="muted">Secure permits, finalize contracts, and orchestrate shipping, insurance, and last‑mile delivery.</p>
          <h3>4) Execution & Scale</h3>
          <p class="muted">Monitor fulfillment, optimize costs, and expand from pilot to steady‑state programs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="media">
